name: Harajuku Dating Paradise ~Nakadashi Banzai~
description:
The protagonist of Harajuku Dating Paradise - Nakadashi Banzai is an energetic guy who loves sex more than anything!

As usual, he sets out in the city of Tokyo trying to pick up someone. What kind of girl will he bump into today?

Win the hearts of 3 lovely ladies: Your normal average nice girl, a lonely housewife, and a spoiled rich girl!
